sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant System
    participant Admin

    User->>System: Upload message/media
    System->>System: Check size constraints
    alt Size within limits
        System->>User: Upload successful
    else Size exceeds limits
        System->>User: Error: Size limit exceeded
        User->>System: Retry with smaller size
    end
    Admin->>System: Update size limits
    System->>Admin: Size limits updated